==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Leaded
<hw>Lead"ed</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Fitted
with lead; set in lead; <as>as, <ex>leaded</ex> windows</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Print.)</fld> <def>Separated by leads, as the lines
of a page.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Leaden</ent>⟦br⟧
